com.android.volley.cronet

Class CronetHttpStack

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.android.volley.toolbox.BaseHttpStack
      • com.android.volley.toolbox.AsyncHttpStack
        • com.android.volley.cronet.CronetHttpStack
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    HttpStack

    public class CronetHttpStack
extends AsyncHttpStack
    A AsyncHttpStack that's based on Cronet's fully asynchronous API for network requests.

    WARNING: This API is experimental and subject to breaking changes. Please see https://github.com/google/volley/wiki/Asynchronous-Volley for more details.
